  <metadata>
    <name>Central Park Walk — 30 min at 10 km/h</name>
    <desc>~5 km walk through Central Park, New York City. Route: West 72nd St entrance → The Mall → Bethesda Fountain → East Drive → Reservoir (south loop) → 86th transverse → West Drive → back to start.</desc>
    <author><name>zaplab-test</name></author>
  </metadata>
